My daughter and myself visited your store on October 27, 2022.
I have NEVER been so offended in my life!
I am from Utah and was seeking something sexy for my daughter.
I had already purchased 4 items before my daughter began trying on Lingerie. First I was told that I could not go into the dressing room with her. I understood the store policy and respected it! I then proceeded to find 3 other pieces of Lingerie, and from the outside of the dressing room, I told my daughter, when she brought those 3 items out, we could exchange for the next three.
All the sudden I m assuming what was the store manager, came up to me in a VERY abrupt accusing manor!
Being very offended I let the staff know, that I could afford to buy ANYTHING  in the store, and if I didn't have class, I would return what I had already purchased!
Of course we opted to take our money elsewhere.
I had purchased 3 items for breast cancer awareness month for a friend, as she is currently Cancer free and I wanted to give her something special. However I am not that lucky. I have stage IV terminal cancer and this was a very meaningful trip, that was soured by poor customer.
It is my opinion, if you want to be successful, replace the staff representing you!
I was an office manager for 25 years prior to my cancer diagnosis , and I am very successful. "Never judge a book by its cover.

Tamara Simcoe
